name: Fly with Tardis
description:
Fly with Tardis

It happened a first time... you escaped from Daleks place with Tardis, but one of the Daleks jumped in Time Vortex with you, and wanna stop you. Can you make Tardis pass to time vortex?

How to play: Hold your Tardis over time vortex until music stops (1min 51sec), and watch out the Dalek.

Keys: Move Tardis with arrow keys.

Notes: It is hard and strongly Dr Who themed game, so i will remove this game instantly from here, if it violates copyrights or something. And i dont take any money this game, its free.
